        <div class="h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center relative overflow-hidden snap-start bg-surface-container-lowest">
            <!-- Background Image -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-30 blur-[1px]" style="background-image: url('/images/slide_future_pillar.webp');"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface-container-lowest via-surface-container-lowest/80 to-surface-container-lowest"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-5"></div>
            
            <div class="max-w-container-max w-full px-gutter relative z-10 text-center">
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-glow-cyan mx-auto mb-stack-lg shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,240,255,0.5)]"></div>
                <span class="font-mono-data text-label-caps text-glow-cyan tracking-[0.2em] mb-stack-sm block">PERSPECTIVAS A FUTURO</span>
                
                <h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-inverse-surface mb-stack-lg max-w-[850px] mx-auto leading-tight">
                    "La calidad, resiliencia y adaptabilidad técnica aseguran que el software seguirá siendo un pilar indispensable de crecimiento."
                </h2>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-stack-lg max-w-[1000px] mx-auto text-left mt-stack-lg border-t border-border-subtle pt-stack-lg">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-headline-md text-glow-cyan mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
